<h1 align="center">&nbsp;<font size="7" face="Arial">Measurement for CBSE</font></h1>
<p>¡¡</p>
<p><b><font face="Arial" size="6">1. How should I size my components?</font></b></p>
<ul>
<font color=red>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  SLOC source lines of code</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Total number of class, if we use object oriented language</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Total number of methods</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Total number of components</font></li>
</font>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p><b><font face="Arial" size="6">2. How detailed should I get?</font></b></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Granularity decides Accuracy</font></li>
